name: Plachatiptai
description: The third piece in my series of “Playing dust”. The Pla-cha-tip-tai in Thai language is mean “democracy”. I created character from each word in ambiguous way.Pla is fish, Cha is tea, Tip in english and Tai is 3 or kidney. I hope one day Thailand will be free from dictatorship and monarch. Digital painting 3000 x 3000 px by @Adce_new 2021
